game launches into command window
default size is 120x30

title screen
user can start game, change settings (optional rules, etc.), exit

settings menu has a list of settings
user selects setting and option

exit just exits the game

start game
user selects division
user selects first then second fighter

game begins

bout display has fighters' stats, endurance, points scored, strategy selected (advanced), ring location, log window, etc.

start of round
user selects styles of E-style fighters (affected numbers are shown) (NOTE: E-style only changes between rounds for simplicity)
(advanced) user selects strategies (affected numbers are shown)

round begins
draw a card every 3.6 seconds and show and apply relevant effect

end of round
user chooses which injuries to work on
end of round effects

game end screen
rematch or return to title screen